so she rejected me.

282
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:36,280
But yes, hypocrisy is in my blood.

283
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:40,360
And we've been selling Deshpande
for the last four generations.

284
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:45,440
