like, Zen space, you know.

290
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:13,240
Calm, mindful,

291
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:15,880
minimalist, feng shui.

292
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,520
And for the walls,

293
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:21,520
I need white and natural wood. And...

294
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:24,320
aromas of the forest.

295
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,640
-And some really soft...
-Whoa, okay.

296
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:29,680
