T-shirts, track pants, bags, slippers.

305
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:53,160
All with Umami branding.

306
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:55,040
We'll see if you want to start...

307
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:57,560
Everyone out. Everyone out. Please.

308
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:00,280
-What?
-I want to talk to you.

309
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:03,880
We don't have two minutes!
We're on a time crunch, so chop-chop!

310
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:06,320
Okay. So, chop-chop.

311
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:08,520
All your ideas are ridiculous.

312
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:13,880
This is not a salon spa.
We're opening a fitness studio.

313
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:16,720
And you don't know
the first thing about it, dude.

314
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:18,960
I want an energetic space,

315
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:21,560
where people would enjoy sweating it out.

316
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:25,160
Not some, like, lah-di-da,
fast fashion, mani pedi,

317
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:27,320
aromas of the forest space, dude.

318
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,320
Mangs.

319
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,160
I say this with a lot of love, okay?

320
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:36,160
But this is why
your loan applications got rejected,

321
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:38,560
