322
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:40,560
And business is in my blood.

323
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,320
I know what I'm doing. Okay?

324
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:47,040
Plus, it's my money, so I think
I should get a say in how we spend this.

325
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:48,160
Right.

326
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:52,080
It's your money, your ideas,
so you take care of everything. Okay?

327
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:55,040
And train my clients as well, okay?
How about that?

328
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:58,960
Enjoy your "fragrances of the forest"
or whatever.

329
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:00,200
Mangs!

330
00:19:01,560 --> 00:19:02,800
Umang...

331
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:07,040
It's so frustrating.
Varun hasn't changed at all.

332
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:09,560
He still finishes all the coffee.

333
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:12,160
He still leaves the toothpaste tube open.

334
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:14,320
He turned the bathroom into his office.

335
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:17,280
Forty-five minute dump
while answering calls, imagine.

336
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:20,000
You know you're no longer
married to him, right?

337
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:21,080
Yeah, obviously.

338
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,760
And you can ask him to leave.

339
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:25,240
Or Kavya might ask him
to leave indefinitely.

340
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:28,240
And then he'll live with you forever.

341
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:31,080
You, Arya and your teenage son, Varun.

342
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,240
Hey, girls! All good?

343
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:36,760
-Hey, Jeh.
-Jeh, I got your text.

344
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:39,520
Listen, five months to move in?

345
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:41,720
Isn't that too long? Can you do something?

346
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:44,320
Damini, let's talk about this later, okay?

347
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,560
Dee?

348
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:54,320
"Mangs is just a small towner
from Ludhiana."

349
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:57,520
Everyone wants to tell me
how to fucking live my life.

350
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,320
My family, Samara and now you!

351
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:01,400
About who I should love, my wedding,

352
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:03,440
