353
00:20:03,520 --> 00:20:06,800
I'm saving your ass.
We all know you're shit with numbers.

354
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:10,280
And you get to decide
that I am shit at numbers

355
00:20:10,320 --> 00:20:13,080
and that you are saving my ass?

356
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:17,560
Wow! Bro, keep your money,
I don't need anyone's charity.

357
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:20,880
Whatever I've achieved thus far,
I've done it myself.

358
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,560
And I'll continue to do it.

359
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,480
Better than you were those bankers.

360
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:27,200
At least,
they didn't set my brain on fire.

361
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:29,080
Free piece of advice to everybody.

362
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:34,080
Never, and I mean never,
go into business with your best friends.

363
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,440
It screws up everything.

364
00:20:37,320 --> 00:20:38,240
Fine!

365
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:45,800
What?

366
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:48,480
Sids, it's Umang's dream.
You have to let go.

367
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,760
You offered to help as a friend.

368
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:53,680
Why are you trying to be her boss?

369
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,560
I'm sorry.

370
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,960
I'm sorry, too.

371
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,480
I'll back off.

372
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:29,320
No, Sids,
I'll find another way. It's fine.

373
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:31,080
But, I'm saying I'll back off.

374
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:38,240
I'll return your money.
With interest. I promise.

375
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:39,480
No way!

376
00:21:39,560 --> 00:21:41,800
It's not a loan. It's an investment.

377
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:43,640
In you and in your dreams.

378
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:45,560
Because I believe in you.

379
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:47,400
Thanks.

380
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:48,560
Don't thank me.

381
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:50,080
