382
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,640
The real language of love.

383
00:21:52,120 --> 00:21:53,040
Cussing.

384
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,720
Witch.

385
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:58,120
Bitch.

386
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,400
Dumbass.

387
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:03,960
What?

388
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:06,560
It means "two potties stuck up your bum."

389
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,320
I love you, too.

390
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:11,040
You don't like potty jokes?

391
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:12,680
No, no. They are the shit.

392
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:15,440
Dee, why are you being so needy?

393
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:19,040
Why do you keep asking Jeh,
"When are you moving in?"

394
00:22:19,120 --> 00:22:21,120
Well, he told me that he will.

395
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:23,800
I'd just like to know when.

396
00:22:24,520 --> 00:22:25,480
Sure, but...

397
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:28,320
you know
that's not gonna solve your problem.

398
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:31,160
Like trying to have a baby
to fix a marriage.

399
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:32,720
Well, that ain't happening.

400
00:22:34,280 --> 00:22:36,520
I'm sorry, I didn't mean it that way.

401
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:38,000
All I'm saying is that

402
00:22:38,760 --> 00:22:39,920
this isn't you.

403
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,600
Me?

404
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:44,240
What is "me," Anj?

405
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:47,480
Unemployed me?

406
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,320
Pregnant me?

407
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:52,120
Banned me. Trolled me.

408
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,360
Writer me.

409
00:22:53,840 --> 00:22:55,680
Writing a thesis on garbage me.

410
00:22:56,800 --> 00:22:58,360
I don't know anymore, Anj.

411
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:04,520
For the first time in my life,
nothing is in my control.

412
00:23:05,800 --> 00:23:09,320
My body or my career. Nothing.

413
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:15,560
The only thing remotely functional
in my life is Jeh and me.

414
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:20,120
So I need to hold on to it, okay?

415
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:21,840
I need it.

416
00:23:25,520 --> 00:23:26,520
Dee.

417
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:28,840
Look at me.

418
00:23:29,320 --> 00:23:31,040
You do you, okay?

419
00:23:31,120 --> 00:23:32,920
Everything will be fine.

420
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:37,600
Okay.

421
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:43,880
-Didn't you have to go to a meeting?
-Yeah, I do.

422
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:48,520
Everything will be fine, Anj.

423
00:23:49,280 --> 00:23:50,560
Yeah.

424
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:11,320
I was thinking...

425
00:24:13,640 --> 00:24:15,640
I'll spend the night at my place.

426
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:20,160
I have to sort out the notice issue.

427
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,480
You can do it from my place, too.

428
00:24:23,080 --> 00:24:24,240
Yeah.

429
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:25,840
