430
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:28,040
I need my thinking spot.

431
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,200
Sure.

432
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:32,840
Come, I'll give you a ride.

433
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:35,680
No, I'll walk. It's a nice evening.

434
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:38,160
Bye.

435
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:59,000
Shashank, things must go back
to how they were.

436
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:02,000
Professionally?

437
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:04,440
Yes.

438
00:25:08,560 --> 00:25:10,560
And how do you propose we do that?

439
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,840
Isn't law our passion?

440
00:25:14,560 --> 00:25:16,960
Isn't it what makes us feel alive?

441
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:20,200
Gives us a reason
to wake up in the morning?

442
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:24,040
Everything else is a distraction.

443
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:32,560
You're right.

444
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:37,320
Let's work with each other, not against.

445
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,800
Exactly.

446
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:58,200
May I?

447
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:00,960
You're stalking me?

448
00:26:02,360 --> 00:26:03,920
Yes. We need to talk.

449
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:04,880
