450
00:26:10,720 --> 00:26:11,600
Me.

451
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:15,160
I'm an honest guy, and I'm a fanboy.

452
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:16,720
Really?

453
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:20,200
Post your exit from Investigator,
I followed you on Twitter.

454
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:22,800
Loved your take on ballot box hack.
Amongst others.

455
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:23,960
"Amongst others"?

456
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,280
I can list them.

457
00:26:26,280 --> 00:26:29,040
EVM hack. Housing scam. Sand mafia.

458
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:31,640
-I don't want compliments.
