459
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:33,440
Stories on potholes and garbage?

460
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:38,080
I'm still following them.

461
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,960
Why don't I see this honesty
in your politics?

462
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:46,720
Your party switches
from centrists, socialists and rightists.

463
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:50,720
You're right. We're coalition champions.

464
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:52,400
That's why I need you.

465
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:55,120
Need me?

466
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:56,800
Plan to sabotage the government?

467
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,280
I plan to make one.

468
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:02,400
Work with me. Help me run my campaign.

469
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:06,160
I want to create a new image,
different from the party line.

470
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:07,880
I wanna walk the hard-line.

471
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:11,920
-You're laughing?
-Did you miss the memo?

472
00:27:12,520 --> 00:27:15,120
I'm persona non-grata
in all political circles.

473
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,840
Left, right, center, up, down.

474
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,600
My career is dead on arrival.

475
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:20,000
Big fucking deal.

476
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:22,520
What's with this loser attitude?

477
00:27:22,600 --> 00:27:25,720
What happened to the firebrand
that was Damini Rizvi Roy?

478
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:29,160
Well, let me think.

479
00:27:29,840 --> 00:27:32,040
I got thrown out of my own news site.

480
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:35,560
My book lead to nationwide protests,
so it got pulled back.

481
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,640
And, oh, wait. One more fuck up.

482
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:40,320
My baby also protested.

483
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:41,920
So, I had a miscarriage.

484
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:45,120
I'm...

485
00:27:46,120 --> 00:27:47,120
I'm sorry.

486
00:27:47,800 --> 00:27:49,480
I didn't know. Really sorry.

487
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:55,160
You just want
my left liberal followers. That's all.

488
00:27:55,800 --> 00:27:59,280
Do you want to just write
about garbage or clean it up, too?

489
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:04,040
Our politics are further
than the North and the South Poles.

490
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:07,280
It's suicide.
Metaphorically and literally.

491
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:08,680
Not just for me,

492
00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:10,120
but for you too.

493
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:12,080
So now, if you'll...

494
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,680
please excuse me.

495
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,760
Damini.

496
00:28:19,760 --> 00:28:22,400
To change the system,
you have to be in it.

497
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:24,880
You can only RT
and comment from the outside.

498
00:28:25,560 --> 00:28:28,000
This is your chance to make a difference.

499
00:28:29,520 --> 00:28:31,880
Now the only thing left for you to ask is,

500
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:34,240
do you have the guts?

501
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,160
To take a chance on me.

502
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,920
On yourself.

503
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:40,880
Don't you miss having the fire inside you?

504
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:44,000
Don't you want it back?

505
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:52,920
This isn't healthy for Arya.

506
00:28:54,120 --> 00:28:55,160
I know.

507
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,760
I just need a couple more days.

508
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:01,560
Just a couple more days, okay?

509
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:03,560
After that,

510
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:05,120
I don't know.

511
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:08,600
Beg, grovel, apologize,
do whatever you have to, just...

512
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:11,080
Make up with Kavya, please.

513
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:12,800
Or Varun, just...

514
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:15,200
Just find a place of your own.

515
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:18,800
Arya needs routine, stability.

516
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:23,480
What if she gets used to living with you?

517
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:25,320
I get it.

518
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:45,520
<i>That's the notion of perfect beauty.</i>

519
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:48,680
<i>So now when people ask me,
"Hey, Siddhi. What's up?"</i>

520
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:51,000
<i>I just tell them, "My self-esteem."</i>

